OL,3,CProgramme listings for
OL,3,CProgramme listings for TUE 3 MAR
OL,4,G2200FMy Week With Lubaina Himid
OL,5,     GAn exploration of Himid's life
OL,6,     Gover seven days after the crew
OL,7,     Gdeparts, as Kate captures candid
OL,8,     Gmoments with just an iPhone.
OL,9,G2300FMy Week With Guerrilla Girls
OL,10,     GKate Bryan explores the lives of
OL,11,     Gthe Guerrilla Girls, a group of
OL,12,     Gart activists who haven't granted
OL,13,     Ga film crew full access to their
OL,14,     Glives and work in over 30 years.
OL,15,G0000FThe Black Italian Renaissance
OL,16,     GUncover the untold story of
OL,17,     GAfrican people who lived during
OL,18,     Gthe Italian Renaissance, often
OL,19,     Gappearing in famous paintings
OL,20,     Gonly to be unacknowledged and
OL,21,     Ghidden in plain sight.
